text: Khandaker Abu Taher is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Tangail-6. ==Career== Taher was elected to parliament from Tangail-6 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
